Info.Title: God's Pocket
Info.Writer: Peter Dexter (novel), Alex Metcalf (screenplay), John Slattery (screenplay)
Info.Actors: Christina Hendricks, Philip Seymour Hoffman, Eddie Marsan, Caleb Landry Jones
Info.Plot: A blue collar worker tries to cover things up when his stepson is killed in a suspicious accident, but a local reporter senses that something's amiss.
